# 🎬 Movie Explorer App

A modern React-based web application that allows users to search for movies, explore trending films, and manage their favorites. The app uses real-time data from [The Movie Database (TMDb) API](https://developers.themoviedb.org/3).

## 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 [View Live on Vercel](https://your-app-url.vercel.app)

---

## 📸 Features

-  **User Login** with basic authentication
-  **Search movies** with real-time API results
-  **View trending movies**
-  **Detailed view** of each movie (overview, cast, genres, rating, trailer)
-  **Light/Dark Mode**
-  **Add/remove movies to/from favorites**
-  Favorites and last search are stored in **localStorage**
- **Infinite scroll** or optional **Load More** button
-  Embedded trailers from YouTube

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, React Router, Context API
- **UI Framework:** Material-UI (MUI)
- **API:** TMDb API (https://api.themoviedb.org/)
- **HTTP Client:** Axios
- **Deployment:** Vercel / Netlify

---

## 🧩 Project Structure

cd movie-explorer

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm start
